<div class="content-page">
  <p class="page-intro">We built Clean Arcade to be the opposite of every ad-infested game site. That philosophy extends to your data.</p>

  <h2>The short version</h2>
  <p>We don't collect your data. No accounts, no cookies, no analytics, no ads. Your game progress is saved locally in your browser. We never see it.</p>

  <h2>What we store</h2>
  <p>Everything stays in your browser's localStorage. Nothing is sent to any server.</p>

  <div class="privacy-table">
    <div class="privacy-table__row">
      <strong>Game saves</strong>
      <span>Stored under keys starting with <code>ca-save-</code></span>
    </div>
    <div class="privacy-table__row">
      <strong>Favorites &amp; recent</strong>
      <span>Stored under <code>ca-favorites</code> and <code>ca-recent</code></span>
    </div>
    <div class="privacy-table__row">
      <strong>Theme</strong>
      <span>Stored under <code>theme</code> (light or dark)</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Third-party services</h2>

  <div class="privacy-table">
    <div class="privacy-table__row">
      <strong>Cloudflare Pages</strong>
      <span>Hosts this website. May collect minimal server logs. <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Privacy policy</a></span>
    </div>
    <div class="privacy-table__row">
      <strong>Bunny Fonts</strong>
      <span>Serves web fonts. GDPR-compliant. <a href="https://bunny.net/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Privacy policy</a></span>
    </div>
    <div class="privacy-table__row">
      <strong>GTranslate</strong>
      <span>Page translation. <a href="https://gtranslate.io/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Privacy policy</a></span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>No ads, no tracking</h2>
  <p>This site contains no advertising, no tracking pixels, no analytics scripts, and no social media trackers.</p>

  <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
  <p>We do not knowingly collect any personal information from anyone, including children. Since we collect no data, there is nothing to protect or delete.</p>

  <h2>Clearing your data</h2>
  <p>To remove all locally stored data, clear your browser's localStorage for this site: Developer Tools &rarr; Application &rarr; Local Storage &rarr; delete entries for this domain.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions about this policy? Email <a href="mailto:{{ meta.email }}">{{ meta.email }}</a>.</p>
</div>
